New table: 50,000,000 rows
Full comparison:
Plain text
Copy code
50M vs 50M rows
Very slow.
Checksum comparison:
Plain text
Copy code
1 number vs 1 number
Very fast.
SQL Used in Azure SQL
Compute checksum for old table.
SQL
Copy code
SELECT CHECKSUM_AGG(BINARY_CHECKSUM(*))
FROM dbo.cff_report
Compute checksum for new table.
SQL
Copy code
SELECT CHECKSUM_AGG(BINARY_CHECKSUM(*))
FROM dbo.cff_report_new
Example result:
Plain text
Copy code
Old table checksum  = 892341234
New table checksum  = 892341234
